        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Future of Water Act of 2022 </strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits the trading of futures contracts in water or water rights. A futures contract is an agreement to buy or sell a commodity or financial instrument at a set price at a specific time.</p>]]>
        </text>
